76174B27.Line28.54239: I told you, the Triune don’t let us in. We’re just hired muscle.

AB8CE6D0.Line22.D5166: Young Dawood caught this one spying. While guarding his post, I might add.

C64D76F4.VoiceDir28.54239: Tired, beaten, bruised. Telling the truth.

DF75D9CF.Line26.D5161: Bastard says the Triune have a hideout near Uldur's Cave. By some “pillar,” he says, but he won’t tell me how to get in.

FBC3129D.VoiceDir22.D5166: Arms folded. Paternal. Hint of pride.
